content: I'm getting this error message when I try and join certain channels?

Are you trying to join the channel for voice purposes or text purposes? Overwhemingly, our channels are text based and we do not converse vocally. The exception is the staff on the stage and watch parties
<@568257600228032512> can you help? I know we don’t have webhook permissions enabled on this server but can you help him to access other channels?

Hi Brad, the error you get is because your server needs webhooks in order to follow this server. 
it looks like you want to see the Announcements from this Discord community all you need to do is turn on notifications for Announcements and you'll see that on your discord dashboard or phone icon. Right-click on Announcements > choose Notification Settings > All messages (or mentions) if you don't want everything.
